== 赛事赞助 ==
1985年开始，诺悠翩雅开始成为意大利[[马术|马术]]运动联合会（{{lang|en|Italian Equestrian Sports Federation}}）的合作伙伴并开始赞助意大利及其他国际骑手。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Leandra Meintjes |title=Loro Piana is the official supplier for the Italian eventing and dressage teams |url=https://www.arabianbusiness.com/press_releases/detail/24773 |publisher={{Link-en|阿拉伯商业周刊|Arabian Business}} |accessdate=2021-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080811235053/https://www.arabianbusiness.com/press_releases/detail/24773 |archivedate=2008-08-11 |location=[[迪拜|迪拜]] |language=en |date=2008-08-05}}</ref>

2006年，诺悠翩雅赞助了[[香港遊艇會|香港賽艇環島大賽]]。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Sail World Asia |title=Loro Piana Around the Island Race 2006 - Hong Kong |url=https://www.sail-world.com/Australia/Loro-Piana-Around-the-Island-Race-2006-Hong-Kong/-29001 |publisher=Sail-World |accessdate=2021-06-04 |language=en |archive-date=2021-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605162311/https://www.sail-world.com/Australia/Loro-Piana-Around-the-Island-Race-2006-Hong-Kong/-29001 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

从2008年开始，诺悠翩雅开始赞助了分别由{{Link-en|船舶国际传媒|Boat International Media}}和{{Link-en|翡翠海岸游艇俱乐部|Yacht Club Costa Smeralda}}组织的两项年度超级游艇赛事。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Alcolm Maclean |title=Claasen sailing yacht Firefly sold |url=https://www.boatinternational.com/yacht-market-intelligence/brokerage-sales-news/claasen-sailing-yacht-firefly-sold |publisher={{Link-en|船舶国际传媒|Boat International Media}} |accessdate=2021-06-05 |location=[[伦敦|伦敦]] |language=en |date=2021-04-09 |archive-date=2021-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605030519/https://www.boatinternational.com/yacht-market-intelligence/brokerage-sales-news/claasen-sailing-yacht-firefly-sold |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Francesca Webster |title=Loro Piana Superyacht Regatta returns to Sardinia this week |url=https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/loro-piana-superyacht-regatta-2021 |publisher=SuperYacht Times |accessdate=2021-06-05 |language=en |date=2021-05-31 |archive-date=2021-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606054955/https://www.superyachttimes.com/yacht-news/loro-piana-superyacht-regatta-2021 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

